    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've heard some people saying that the mining for wind turbine parts like lithium and rare earth metals is actually way worse for the environment than just sticking with gas. if you look at the total damage to the land and ecosystems, is wind actually \"cleaner\" or is that just a label?",
